            "reviews": "“I just made a spell that lets me shoot rocks that I can control with my mind and I’m using it to squish a bunch of angry water mages.”<br><a href=\"http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/09/02/tricks-and-tomes-will-break-your-bones-runers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Rock, Paper, Shotgun</a><br><br>“Runers is a fantastic game. It boasts solid gameplay with tons of replayability. The game is difficult, but in a rewarding way.”<br>8.5 / 10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.capsulecomputers.com.au/2014/09/runers-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Capsule Computers</a><br><br>“Runers is an immensely fun game for fans of the dungeon crawler to get excited about. Hardcore gamers will love what LGK Games have created with the diversity and variety of both the character selection and the enthralling gameplay.”<br>7 / 10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.godisageek.com/2014/09/runers-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >God Is A Geek</a><br>",
